{"tid":2099610,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屁股都有假，我屌！屁股移位　楊冪被質疑裝假籮","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:41:52.000Z","uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd56eb68ef74687cd5e646e60381d28720c5922","tid":2099610,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>蜜桃臀係流嘅？屁股移位　楊冪被質疑裝假籮<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=97f65cba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=cd268b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜜桃臀是這樣煉成的？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_02b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=79dc7794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個樣嚇親唔少人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=f8f912b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又平又扁？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=c9e125c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影靚相就變翹臀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_05b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=48c440e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屁股位置有啲詭異！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_06b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=10dae9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臀部疑似移位&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_07b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=91ff8cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟真相係點？<br />\n<br />\n大陸女星楊冪早前面部意外崩壞照嚇驚網民，雖然佢之後嘅旗袍Look為佢扳回一城，點知櫈都未坐暖，又被網民質疑「裝假籮」！<br />\n<br />\n社交網流傳楊冪私下被粉絲影低嘅生活照，發覺佢個Pat Pat比較扁平，而出席公開活動時就有好曲線，名副其實嘅蜜桃臀！<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有從後台方向影佢背部嘅照片，見佢屁股位置有啲詭異，網民話疑似臀部「移位」，質疑佢平時出席公開場係裝咗假屁股！<br />\n<br />\n有網民就直言「女明星為了美也是拼了」、「知道有假胸原來還有假屁股」、「為了拍照效果好點沒甚麼很正常​​」，亦有人為楊冪平反，話只係影得衰啫！"},{"pid":"b6c0aadf48fbc8c87625bf42780b4b67f5a40b05","tid":2099610,"uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b846cc35c13f21da21cb39a853aa5191ddb2fd1","tid":2099610,"uid":282930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"做假大國有乜做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499edd1c5fa975dee6eb5c1b4c8a31f5219451d3","tid":2099610,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"貼百份報link，想洗淡重要嘢？收皮啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"fa42b4c92f55a405d9bfa0afef0c63d49f38571e","tid":2099610,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"假尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796276ab5b81c5a7bc305e6994ee9dc0912beb94","tid":2099610,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:50:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，買件衫狙我3年仲要屈我五毛，你都幾勁品喔柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af4096a33878d3292acaa90c0e7065bf51cdf73","tid":2099610,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"佢咁瘦,有撚屎忽咩其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb2aeccacb898d3517c3549406436a0efd909c","tid":2099610,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7af4096a33878d3292acaa90c0e7065bf51cdf73","tid":2099610,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"佢咁瘦,有撚屎忽咩其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"假屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537fb52ffc8ea6dd0fa805f361c46c9029ba3180","tid":2099610,"uid